downloadTitle: Microsoft Lync Server 2010 Reference: Call Data Recording and Quality of Experience Database Schema
downloadDescription: This document describes the call detail recording (CDR) and the Quality of Experience (QoE) databases schemas in Microsoft Lync Server 2010.
detailsSection: This document describes the call detail recording (CDR) and the Quality of Experience (QoE) databases schemas in Microsoft Lync Server 2010.
